Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:15.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,25 YEARS AGO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.06,0:02:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rewinding to 25 years ago...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A little before the Great Pirate Era began...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everybody having a good time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am glad that I followed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!\NWhy are you saying such a thing now, idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must thank you instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.24,0:03:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're drinking too much!\NControl yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!\NI won't take advice from a drunken doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm concerned about your health!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lie there quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.74,0:04:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the cure for stupidity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the Land of Wano?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, there is still something major left to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything we can do to help, Oden?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need a hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can lend one, Oden-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!\NYou'll get in his way instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Oden-{\i1}san{\i0}. I'm sure I can help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rayleigh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Redtaro, Buggyjiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We, the Kozuki, must do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've asked you so many times,\Nwhy do you call me "jiro (second son)"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.23,0:05:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let it go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. The Kozuki, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned a lot through this journey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wondered\Nwhy the Land of Wano closed its door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left the country by my own choice, so I won't say\Na selfish thing like, "Let me become the Shogun"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I must pass this will on at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:06:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With my great retainers that I left behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.47,0:06:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will open up the Land of Wano!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will wait for the "future"\Nthat will come more than 20 years from now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it, Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will do it, Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:25.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,25 YEARS LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now 25 years have passed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:32.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,LAND OF WANO ACT THREE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:42.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,OROCHI
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:57.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,HABU PORT, HAKUMAI
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orochi-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Rendezvous Port!\NThe Land of Wano Act Three Begins!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is a good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that view!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a perfect day for a banquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Orochi-{\i1}sama{\i0} is even favored by good weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, Kyoshiro will stay at the capital to look after it!\NTell him we are counting on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor guy! He can't attend the banquet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This Habu Port in Hakumai\Nis known as the largest port in the Land of Wano.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maple trees line the giant pier\Nwhich projects from the shore into the sea,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:08:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the lovely scene of fluttering red leaves\Nsends ships off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring {\i1}sake{\i0}! Let's have a cup\Nwhile admiring those red leaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orochi-{\i1}sama{\i0}, you should not drink\Nuntil you see Kaido-{\i1}sama{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares! I know he is drunk, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a big banquet with 30 thousand guests!\NLet's have a great time as always!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On the night of the annual Fire Festival,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the two leaders who rule the Land of Wano\Ncome together at Onigashima.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And they throw a big banquet\Nat which all of Orochi's army and Kaido's army gather.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:43.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,FLOWER CAPITAL ON THE DAY OF THE FIRE FESTIVAL
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! It's already started!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I don't like the way my bangs look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drink! Sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.75,0:10:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Fire Festival in the capital today!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only day we're allowed to drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll drink hard and have a good time today!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.94,0:10:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky's so clear!\NWe'll see a beautiful full moon tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The seasons of each region of the Land of Wano\Ndiffer wildly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:54.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,TOKAGE PORT
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The weather also varies tremendously\Nby location.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:11:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At that same moment,\Nat the rendezvous point, Tokage Port...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:11:01.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,AT THE SAME MOMENT\NTHE RENDEZVOUS POINT, TOKAGE PORT
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a single ship is in sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the four thousand soldiers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am positive we conquered Udon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one is there at the labor camp, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like this port was attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears the cat couldn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Smail is not responding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot contact anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At twilight on the day of the Fire Festival,\Nat Tokage Port!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the rendezvous port!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.81,0:12:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why hasn't anyone come?!\NWhere did they go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been only a day...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this all about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something happened to everyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heave ho! Heave ho! Heave ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dance! Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the annual Fire Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.33,0:12:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you let loose\Nand burn off some stress tonight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}dono{\i0}, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyogoro-{\i1}dono{\i0}, please respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dogstorm Musketeers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law-{\i1}dono{\i0}!\NJibuemon of Kibi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are Kozuki Oden's retainers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From 20 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came from 20 years ago\Nto avenge our lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should have died at that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we came to die for a cause!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it takes more than just our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy has 30 thousand soldiers!\NWe need help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody, please help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody, respond!\NPlease help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.23,0:13:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, Kin'emon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the sky and sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are already abandoned even by heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something must have happened to everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:26.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,TWO DAYS AGO
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rewinding to two days before the Fire Festival...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.27,0:14:30.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,AMIGASA VILLAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm-hm. Now we have 4,200 soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am glad... I am glad that they joined us...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you for your work!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Use the remaining time for\Ntravel and preparations.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you at the rendezvous port!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:59.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ITACHI PORT, KURI
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finish fixing enough ships\Nto carry five thousand people!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.56,0:15:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring those ships to the port by the appointed time!\NCan you do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Count on us, Big Bro Franosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:17.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ITACHI PORT\NAMIGASA VILLAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we'll meet up with our friends\Nin Amigasa Village,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and come by the Sunny on that day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll leave the rest to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Thank you for helping us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.71,0:15:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are great shipwrights!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! Let's take those Animal Kingdom Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and kick their asses, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:43.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,UDON
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much timber we have,\Nit's never enough! Cut up everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.81,0:15:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ocho's group will bring\Nswords and the like from Ringo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll craft armor from whatever we have!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if they're usable,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we have tons of weapons and those sorts of things\Nfor export here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:15:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we go to the rendezvous point too early,\Nwe will draw people's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:04.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,KIBI
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...on the morning of that day, the Shogun's procession\Nwill wind from the capital to the port.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:09.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,HABU PORT            FLOWER CAPITAL
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once they leave for Onigashima,\Nthe Fire Festival will take place in the capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will pay us any mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Two birds..."\NWe better get there before twilight...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:22.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,UDON
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But some officials will still be on the mainland!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:25.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ITACHI PORT
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:29.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,KIBI
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot let them report to Onigashima,\Nso stay alert the whole way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you allowing us to use these?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.57,0:16:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It's a samurai helmet!\NI wanna show it to Usopp, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're warriors!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your enemy is that ill-famed Kaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.04,0:16:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all prepared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That loser...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is about to be sliced up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think we'll lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobro and the others look good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how cute. Just like bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bugs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Cute...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you wear one, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.53,0:17:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it'll just slow me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since your bounty is so low!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna fight?! I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try it, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you fools doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:18:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orochi said that it's winter\Nat the entrance to Onigashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is it cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.49,0:18:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "entrance"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.19,0:18:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mainland of the Land of Wano\Nhas different seasons in different areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.24,0:18:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're coated with fur,\Nso we're okay with cold weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:16.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,DOGSTORM THREE MUSKETEERS
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, for us, the weather is more crucial...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:18.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,CONCELOT     SHISHILIAN     GIOVANNI
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.34,0:18:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...than the season!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's supposed to be a full moon that day,\Nbut if it hides behind the clouds, it's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If all Minks transform like Carrot,\Nthat'll help us a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garchu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Sulong transformation\Nwill depend on luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more important to have\NMaster Cat Viper and Guardians here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Mom is here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Jimbei isn't here yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to him, we got away from Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you at the Land of Wano!\NCome at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.19,0:19:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He joined us after he settled things!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're happy to have him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've still got time... He'll come!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll come!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:20:02.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,EBISU TOWN, OUTSIDE OF THE FLOWER CAPITAL
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:20:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys! Come here! Ushimitsu Kozo came!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no talk of a robbery in the capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the only person who would do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't take part in the Fire Festival tomorrow,\Nbut let's drink water with these!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We burned down the mountain bandit's mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But instead of seeking revenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they keep stealing tons of food from our farm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:25.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,OKOBORE TOWN, KURI
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you guys have something to do with it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.60,0:20:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard samurai are preparing to make a raid...\NIs that why, maybe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, we can't let them know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys whispering about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will guide you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:52.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,OTSURU - KIN'EMON'S WIFE
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So do not hurt anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Otsuru-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guide me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will see once you get there.\NIt is a little far though...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You must need tons of food\Nbecause you are with so many allies!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.81,0:21:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh, Kin-{\i0}san{\i1}?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You are here in the Land of Wano, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was stunned when I saw Kikunojo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kin-{\i0}san{\i1}...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kin-{\i0}san{\i1}, let me handle this!\NI will draw their attention!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.69,0:21:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will not let them search for you all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kin-{\i0}san{\i1}... Take back Kozuki's country!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Otsuru-{\i1}san{\i0}!\NYou don't have to cover for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay now!\NWe just wanted to eat as much as we wanted before we die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.39,0:21:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.16,0:21:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's you guys who did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:22:00.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,TOKAGE PORT, UDON, THE PRESENT
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.18,0:22:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a small boat...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.43,0:22:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.35,0:22:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Dogstorm?! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.41,0:22:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this another day, Kin'emon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.67,0:22:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is not an option...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.62,0:22:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kin-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me, Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.42,0:22:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kin-{\i1}sama{\i0}, we can't do this tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.29,0:22:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must do it tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.17,0:22:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that, Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.93,0:22:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has got to be tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.98,0:23:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An incident had already taken place\Nthe night before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.41,0:23:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Sunny is blown up!\NNot knowing of Luffy and the others' safety{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.06,0:23:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Akazaya samurai move on with\Ntheir lord's words in their hearts!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.01,0:23:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The hero of the age, Oden, went his own way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.19,0:23:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, how he lived replays\Nlike cherry blossoms taking flight!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece! "The Number-One\NSamurai in the Land of Wano! Here comes Kozuki Oden!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.37,0:23:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.65,0:23:49.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,